===========================================================
Permission Apply 
1- chmod - owner group for all others but we can not give permission on any particular user or any group 

2- setfacl - it is an advance concept of chmod command , cos we can give permission on any particular user or any goup 


. No acl on it 
+  basic permission + advance permission ==> chmod + setfacl 

